title: Freddie Hubbard - The Black Angel (1970) Atlantic/Collectables
description:
FREDDIE HUBBARD - THE BLACK ANGEL

1. Spacetrack (Freddie Hubbard) [16:56]
2. Eclipse (Freddie Hubbard) [8:16]
3. The Black Angel (Kenny Barron) [8:17]
4. Gittin' Down (Freddie Hubbard) [6:38]
5. Coral Keys (Walter Bishop, Jr.) [5:20]

All the arrangements are by Freddie Hubbard

Freddie Hubbard - trumpet
James Spaulding - alto sax & flute
Kenny Barron - piano & electric piano
Reggie Workman - bass
Louis Hayes - drums
Carlos "Potato" Valdes - congas & maracas

Recorded at Regent Sound Studios, NYC

Originally released in 1970 as Atlantic SD 1549

2006 Rhino/Collectables
